DOC.HEADLINE: LAGUNA NIGUEL SURFERS ADVANCE AT PISMO BEACH
DOC.TEXT: Pat O ' Connell and Vince De La Pena of Laguna Niguel advanced to today ' s quarterfinals of the $ 23 # 600 Bud Surf Tour event Saturday at Pismo Beach . De La Pena finished first in his third-round heat , and O ' Connell finished second . Jeff Deffenbaugh and Jay Larson of Huntington Beach , Jason Senn , Mike Parsons and Dino Andino of San Clemente , Tim Reardon of Dana Point and Shane Stoneman of San Juan Capistrano were eliminated in the third round .
